nt/entertainment/20201205/bkn-20201205151935061-1205_00862_001.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=東華2020︱廖慧儀負面新聞纏身缺席直播　照樣表演到功夫勁離奇 |url=https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/558085/%E6%9D%B1%E8%8F%AF2020-%E5%BB%96%E6%85%A7%E5%84%80%E8%B2%A0%E9%9D%A2%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%BA%8F%E8%BA%AB%E7%BC%BA%E5%B8%AD%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD-%E7%85%A7%E6%A8%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%BC%94%E5%88%B0%E5%8A%9F%E5%A4%AB%E5%8B%81%E9%9B%A2%E5%A5%87 |work=香港01 |date=2020-12-05 |accessdate=2020-12-05 |archive-date=2022-04-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220403052758/https://www.hk01.com/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82%E5%A8%9B%E6%A8%82/558085/%E6%9D%B1%E8%8F%AF2020-%E5%BB%96%E6%85%A7%E5%84%80%E8%B2%A0%E9%9D%A2%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E%E7%BA%8F%E8%BA%AB%E7%BC%BA%E5%B8%AD%E7%9B%B4%E6%92%AD-%E7%85%A7%E6%A8%A3%E8%A1%A8%E6%BC%94%E5%88%B0%E5%8A%9F%E5%A4%AB%E5%8B%81%E9%9B%A2%E5%A5%87 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。直至2021年11月，她才開始回復演藝工作。

